Note [Suggest NegativeLiterals]
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
If you write
  x :: Int8
  x = -128
it'll parse as (negate 128), and overflow.  In this case, suggest NegativeLiterals.
We get an erroneous suggestion for
  x = 128
but perhaps that does not matter too much.

